{"tid":2358100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普發出付上辭職信範本的備忘 提醒內閣須按慣例請辭","createTime":"2021-01-08T01:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T02:25:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4e06f9a5019e60ffed7052b520e311e4ea6322","tid":2358100,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"白宮向內閣官員發備忘 提醒須按慣例請辭<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，特朗普政府已經向內閣官員發出備忘，提醒他們要按慣例在新政府就職日中午前請辭。備忘由白宮副幕僚長兼總統助理利德爾向內閣和行政部門主管發出，內容提到必須採取恰當措施，確保權力有序交接，並付上辭職信範本。消息人士指早在上月已經有官員提出要因應政府換屆而辭職，但被阻止；今次的備忘顯示特朗普政府已經準備好離開白宮。<br />\n<br />\n美國憲法並無規定現任官員須在新政府上任前辭職，但一般由總統任命而未有固定任期的官員都會請辭。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2373899&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=3346e082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373899</a>"},{"pid":"941f9d0c54991d72a0bf29b20c480050d81b4d0d","tid":2358100,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0507916ea96921e0c8a23afe13c01e7cf7ca31","tid":2358100,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"支持pompeo唔辭職霸住個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be961f7b4655da09c349d92c6c6a8d24361bb371","tid":2358100,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"當死左嗰4個支持者係咩？<br />\n屌那星侵咁做真係白白送死"},{"pid":"62c3e1d2d615c586f438eba021e4d634ca6ce03b","tid":2358100,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be961f7b4655da09c349d92c6c6a8d24361bb371","tid":2358100,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"當死左嗰